              <h1>The Global Carbon Project</h1>
              <p>The Global Carbon Project (GCP) integrates knowledge of greenhouse gases for human activities and the Earth system. Our projects include global budgets for three dominant greenhouse gases &mdash; carbon dioxide, methane, and nitrous oxide &mdash; and complementary efforts in urban, regional, cumulative, and negative emissions.</p>
